DisplayName: Metal Detect
Summary: Turn your smartphone into a metal detector using the built-in magnetometer sensor.
Description: Metal Detect is an open source Android application that uses your smartphone's built-in magnetometer sensor to detect metal objects. Simply move your phone near metal surfaces and the app will detect changes in the magnetic field.
This app is a fork of the original Metal Detector app by Ian Baldwin Posedio, created with permission and gratitude for making the original code open source.
Features:
- Real-time magnetic field strength measurement in μT (microTesla)
- Audio and haptic feedback when metal is detected
- Support for most Android devices with magnetometer sensors
- Light and dark theme support
- Flashlight feature (if device has flash)
Note: This app is designed for entertainment purposes only.
